  "stem": "<p>The circumference of the base of a right circular cylinder is <em><math alttext=\"20 pi\"><mrow><mn>20</mn></mrow><mi>&#960;</mi></math>&nbsp;</em>meters, and the height of the cylinder is <math alttext=\"6\"><mn>6</mn>\n</math> meters. What is the volume, in cubic meters, of the cylinder?</p>",
